Package: libyadifa-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libdnscore0 (=${binary:Version}), libdnsdb0 (=${binary:Version}), libdnszone0 (=${binary:Version})
Description: yadifa development libraries and header files
 YADIFA (Yet Another DNS Implementaion For All) is a lightweight authoritative
 Name Server with DNSSEC capabilities. It has been developed from scratch by
 the .eu TLD registry.
 .
 This package contains archive-style libraries and header files for
 libdnscore0, libdnsdb0 and libdnszone0
